{"tid":1731053,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"理大譴責佔領校園人士暴力行為 促所有人離開","createTime":"2019-11-17T15:51:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T16:34:32.000Z","uid":133680,"like":9,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"7568ab27a345804ad9b56a8ab1fc322c4bd9d97f","tid":1731053,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:51:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2727658870630596/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2727658870630596%2F&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=f4b75f0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2727658870630596/</a><br />\n<br />\n【理大譴責佔領校園人士暴力行為 促所有人離開】<br />\n<br />\n理工大學發出緊急通告，指理大校園連日被示威者佔據，校園設施和設備被大規模嚴重破壞，激進人士於校園及鄰近地區的違法活動及暴力行為愈益激烈，包括破壞了多個實驗室並取去危險化學品。校方強調，大學是創造知識、培育人才之所，絕不是政治爭議的戰場，更不應被捲入暴力對峙的旋渦。理大嚴正譴責佔領校園人士的所有違法和暴力行為，並要求他們立即離開理大校園。<br />\n<br />\n校方非常關注有關的激進非法活動持續升級，不單對校園安全構成嚴重的威脅，更令復課無期。校方再次敦促所有人士，包括學生及教職員，從速離開校園。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-17-2019/57610\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F11-17-2019%2F57610&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=1eceb2e4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/11-17-2019/57610</a><br />\n<br />\n#理大 #紅隧<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=9c9e143d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=be55a534\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise2&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=07665873\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise2</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血主持育成計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2F%3Fview%3Draise&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=7b5ecb8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/?view=raise</a><br />\n<br />\n《熱血時報》 iOS，Android 同步抗共，歡迎下載：<br />\n<br />\niPhone<br />\n<a href=\"https://apple.co/2IfgPoP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapple.co%2F2IfgPoP&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=42eb722f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://apple.co/2IfgPoP</a><br />\n<br />\nAndroid<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2HqB4Q4&d=RPOps9CZsjru%2Bb3lYBIKGtAAr5%2FwdiPol2qeWm%2BM8v8%3D&h=0e61ca79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2HqB4Q4</a><br />\n--------------------<br />\n成功之前，我們絕對不要放棄夢想！<br />\nTill our dreams come true, we'll fight on."},{"pid":"11557c3cf99ca9ca652d7f20ef86316a65932555","tid":1731053,"uid":148023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:51:50.000Z","msg":"想救理大?<br />\n不妨睇一睇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1730983\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1730983</a>"},{"pid":"d71ae8dbd9484348edd3b1da18e1e4b2f7598e43","tid":1731053,"uid":4618,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:52:22.000Z","msg":"點走"},{"pid":"32268e1b24d2455e3be887213bd26cdf48748fe4","tid":1731053,"uid":56138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T15:52:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\